msgid ""
"Select the fonts to use for the text in the image CAPTCHA. Apart from "
"the provided defaults, you can also use your own TrueType fonts "
"(filename extension .ttf) by putting them in %fonts_library_general or "
"%fonts_library_specific."
msgstr ""
"Selecciona as fontes para usar no texto do CAPTCHA da imaxe. Ademais "
"das fontes predeterminadas proporcionadas, tamén podes usar as túas "
"propias fontes TrueType (extensión do nome do ficheiro .ttf) "
"colocándoas en %fonts_library_general ou %fonts_library_specific."

