"list. Note, that the captcha point <em>default challenge</em> will be "
"used as the challenge type for the created CAPTCHA challenges."
msgstr ""
"Engade CAPTCHA a todos os formularios de Drupal, independentemente da "
"lista de Puntos Captcha. Teña en conta que o punto captcha "
