"%capital_name contains terms with multiple parents. Drag and drop of "
"terms with multiple parents is not supported, but you can re-enable "
"drag-and-drop support by editing each term to include only a single "
"parent."
msgstr ""
"%capital_name contén termos con varios pais. Non se admite arrastrar "
"e soltar termos con varios pais, pero podes volver activar o soporte "
"de arrastrar e soltar editando cada termo para incluír só un único "
"pai."

